{"tid":1742950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔駛理風向，請獨立思考","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T05:39:40.000Z","uid":191487,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb5ee6eb787ecc989f39e7e64d80d95459e3661","tid":1742950,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"連登呢兩日既風向，主要有住以下情況 :<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 選舉撚</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 為左區選馬上煞停所有行動。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 行動撚</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 食人血饅頭正一政棍，選舉無意思，繼續搞大佢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 民意撚</span></ins></strong><br />\n- 民意已達極限。<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過，其實所有風都係同一班人吹 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要達成最佳分化效果，唔係講一邊既說話，而係多邊分化，乜都講。製造稻草人，製造對立，咁先有得分化。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">事實係 : </span></strong></ins><br />\n-<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 體制內外都係戰線，全撚部都要贏</strong></span>，無話邊樣唔重要。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 美國人權法案係一仗，區選又點會唔係重要戰役?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 即使你不認同選舉會帶來改變，也<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請不要讓這個利益塊板拱手送給對手</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 魔法神獸都唔割，會因為交通問題就割既可能性有幾大?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 紅隧死左，已經等同日日黎明，有心搞既自己搭車個陣搞就得，仲駛乜上黎吹雞?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要大家獨立思考，我好有信心呢D藍絲式既單邊宣傳撥火根本動搖唔到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地多線作賽，要識得分配主力。呢幾日應該集中做D乜先可以帶來最大效益，留番俾大家思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n記得兄弟爬山，各自努力，不分化不割蓆不篤灰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係我就上少D連登，睇少幾個無營養既post，呢幾日搞多D文宣，順手又可以差下電。<br />\n貼下牆，整下長輩圖，提醒下各位選民，邊個黨派有份支持送中，邊個假獨立真建制，送撚走哂佢地再繼續開佢老母波。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506644edb5830f092f50c751b365e8280bcafae1","tid":1742950,"uid":211004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:07:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"25d8f03902ec8d4817a7b5a6ee85939221600e92","tid":1742950,"uid":3865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"f40a60c54976478d9bbf2dcf2f345d32baf89db1","tid":1742950,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:13:35.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"72c74dc33e2cc887401e52c36d5f53e936d32155","tid":1742950,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:15:29.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"d4836f9ba3559d01071cb3d4665103837565de89","tid":1742950,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=1069de6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6860f518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=77ae51f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=746b74f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"5a98c2763aa03ef18acaec902bd55ed87beb80f7","tid":1742950,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7df034c2b7566ad6628e6afaf47e55777ab83a","tid":1742950,"uid":284642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"大家諗法相似<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪唔記左區選？係咪唔記得左長期作戰既重要性？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742908</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73ca33b34209430fa69bbf2623335c3c1bd07427","tid":1742950,"uid":8562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:17:08.000Z","msg":"upp"},{"pid":"b674bc315ae5aacc9ed2d0a116fd95e00d0dbbfc","tid":1742950,"uid":36761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"體制內外都係戰線，全撚部都要贏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237a7a58fc1838d14685c6b6a49e269651245e8b","tid":1742950,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"重要既事，同我講3次 : <br />\n<br />\n體制內外都係戰線，全撚部都要贏<br />\n體制內外都係戰線，全撚部都要贏<br />\n體制內外都係戰線，全撚部都要贏"},{"pid":"9051bdfc2c1205ab26eaa1fad9e89d0b3119292a","tid":1742950,"uid":60977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"諗下下步行動仲實際<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68638c0bf6264f4404c6a068b