plyTime":"2019-11-21T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"同意，上連登就淨係睇同推有用post，唔好俾人帶風向。講多無謂，行動最實際。"},{"pid":"b417b7f9e5cc0643216e90903ef7e57c183d89af","tid":1742950,"uid":36807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:57:05.000Z","msg":"星期日投票<br />\n<br />\n贏👉🏻繼續抗爭<br />\n冇贏👉🏻繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38feb45d808873a0cc08c15ee2fe156d6fcd794","tid":1742950,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"呢個咪又係風向po"},{"pid":"7fc14c84c973f8250b5536ca3b2a11a35f13e3e8","tid":1742950,"uid":47110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n正視聽"}]}